<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="invest-v">invest <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'vest/    美 /ɪn'vest/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>投资；投入：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have <strong>invested</strong> all my money <strong>in</strong> that company.
我已把所有的钱都投给了那家公司。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>invested</strong> all my energy <strong>in</strong> my job.
我把全部精力投入到工作中。</p></div></div>